{"id":148092,"type":6,"name":"亡命天涯","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/34/40/148092_Exeyp.jpg","summary":"清光绪末年，为人正直的禁军统领荣仁杰与爱妻方琳过着幸福的生活，由于揭发了康亲王博格多以无辜小孩为慈禧研制长生不老药，博格多为保秘密，迫仁杰家破人亡，仁杰亦被送往慈禧墓中陪葬。 20 年后，生性疏懒的华光和沉迷医学的余慕华二人，误闯慈禧墓中，救出仁杰，逃出墓穴的仁杰竟成为长生不死的异人，二人得知仁杰的异能后，华光想藉此谋财，而慕华却一心想着医学研究，故闹出不少笑话。仁杰面对 20 年后的社会难以适应，万念俱灰，恰街头巧遇一位与前妻同一模样的女子林若冰，认定是妻子转世，于是决心再续前缘，可是他在得悉妻子未死后，找回昔日爱侣，二人见面愰如隔世，仁杰外表未变，但方琳已入老年。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>亡命天涯</li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/16626\">劉松仁</a>、<a href=\"/person/19691\">莫少聰</a>、<a href=\"/person/16415\">關詠荷</a>、<a href=\"/person/19717\">吳家麗</a></li><li><span>配角: </span><a href=\"/person/19718\">洪欣</a>、<a href=\"/person/16731\">連凱</a>、<a href=\"/person/16740\">陈龙</a></li><li><span>集数: </span>34</li><li><span>开始: </span>1997年</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>中国大陆</li><li><span>导演: </span>梁本熙</li>","eps":[{"id":570224,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/570224","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":570225,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/570225","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":570226,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/570226","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":570227,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/570227","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":570228,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/570228","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":570229,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/570229","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":570230,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/570230","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":570231,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/570231","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duratio